OL,4,G0530FThis is BBC Four
OL,5,G1858FThis is BBC Four
OL,6,G1900FNature: The Classical Collection
OL,7,     GThe natural world has always been
OL,8,     Ga powerful inspiration to
OL,9,     Gcomposers, and this programme
OL,10,     Gtakes us on an evocative journey
OL,11,     Gthrough some of the best-loved
OL,12,     Gmusical responses.
OL,13,G1915FA Wild Year
OL,14,     GIn the north east of England lies
OL,15,     Ga wild and remote moorland. This
OL,16,     Gancient landscape of heather-clad
OL,17,     Guplands and sheltered dales is
OL,18,     Ghome to red grouse and tough
OL,19,     Gmoorland sheep.
