OL,4,G2015FRomeo and Juliet with Rudolf
OL,5,     FNureyev and Margot Fonteyn
OL,6,     GMargot Fonteyn and Rudolf Nureyev
OL,7,     Gstar in the Royal Ballet's Romeo
OL,8,     Gand Juliet. From 1977.
OL,9,G2215FThe Magic of Dance with Margot
OL,10,     FFonteyn
OL,11,     GMargot Fonteyn looks at the work
OL,12,     Gof some of the greatest of the
OL,13,     Gpioneers, from the Commedia
OL,14,     Gdell'Arte in 17th-century Italy
OL,15,     Gto Martha Graham in 20th-century
OL,16,     GAmerica.
